<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>dāng nǐ tà shàng zhè tiáo lù 迦南979</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dāng nǐ tà shàng zhè tiáo lù, huì tīng dào hěn duō de shēng yīn. nǐ yī dìng yào zǐ xì tīng, shēng yīn lái zì hé fāng.
 dāng nǐ tà shàng zhè tiáo lù, huì yù dào hěn duō lù kǒu. nǐ yī dìng yào zǐ xì biàn rèn, lù tōng xiàng hé fāng.
 zhǔ shì nǐ de mù yáng rén, nǐ shì zhǔ de xiǎo yáng. nǐ yào tīng mù rén de shēng yīn, jǐn gēn zài zhǔ shēn páng.
 tā shì nǐ shēng mìng de quán yuán, xiàng tā huān rán qǔ shuǐ. ràng shēng mìng zhī hé, liú xiàng wàn bāng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>979</hymn_number>
</song>